Semi buffet price is reasonable. With range from 2xx to 400
Great Atmosphere, let down by the average food though
Quality food in good bargain

No free service zone now and the menu didn't change much.  This restaurant wasn't big... or we may describe it was small. We therefore prefer spending at  another restaurant on the same floor since their price was quiet expensive.

reviews.text: Staff were kind and helpful. The service is really great,foods were good too. The place is cozy and child friendly. You can easily access through lift.
揀咗個半自助餐，啲前菜選擇唔多，但都幾好味。啲甜品選擇都幾好，呢到重有凍蝦、青口同細蜆都幾好食。
麻麻地！沒有想像中那麼好吃！也不是太差，但我不會再去！
鱈魚味道清淡合宜，安格斯牛扒肉汁丰富，自助沙津ok😄😉

半自助餐 主菜羊肋吃了幾口 非常少肉的 
不知有否 體會食客感受
環境不錯 甜品可以
